From b622170320ab6d98d86c69174a0d3ae05113a777 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 19:10:27 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] launcher: fix top gap, bleed wallpaper under system bars,
 modernize build

- LayoutViewModel.calculateDesktop: drop remainHeight/2 from marginTop on
  phone so the app grid hugs the status bar instead of self-centering
  within the reserved 6-row area (previously left ~81vp of empty space
  above the first row on the Volla X23/mimir form factor).
- EntryView: expandSafeArea(SYSTEM, [TOP, BOTTOM]) on the background
  container so the default wallpaper extends under status/nav bars.
- Switch default wallpaper from jpg to png.
- Replace hvigorfile.js with hvigorfile.ts (hvigor 5.18.5 rejects the
  old .js form with "The root node is not yet available for build").
- Drop the vendored hvigorw/hvigorw.bat wrappers and local.properties;
  rely on the system-PATH hvigorw and per-developer local settings.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Change-Id: I6645ae0fc76ede2718b4da330472050943327ea2
